# Invite links route through the invite-preview function, which injects
# PER-TABLE OG tags ("ElleBell's Table · 2/4 seated") into the static
# invite page — and always answers 200 (crawlers refuse to card a 404).
# These are REWRITES: the browser URL keeps /join/CODE, so the page's
# pathname-parsing JS still reads the code. /og/* serves the per-table
# card PNG (falls back to /assets/og-card.png for unknown codes).
# Every other unknown path still falls through to 404.html with a 404.
/join/*      /.netlify/functions/invite-preview?kind=join&code=:splat     200
/invite/*    /.netlify/functions/invite-preview?kind=invite&code=:splat   200
/og/join/*   /.netlify/functions/og-image?kind=join&code=:splat           200
/og/invite/* /.netlify/functions/og-image?kind=invite&code=:splat         200
